This paper is primarily focused on malware detection using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also extensively uses document classification techniques and support vector machines, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also discusses the optimization of the machine learning algorithm, which is a common topic in software engineering (cs.SE) research. Finally, the paper deals with feature extraction and classification, which are topics in data science (cs.DS).
